author: jleroux
msg: A patch from Deepak Dixit "Demo data in OFBiz that explain "My Group" concept. (https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/OFBIZ-2435) - OFBIZ-2435

Extend DEV and TESTING group to add few more groups that will be teams. These teams will be a party group in the role of Internal Organization.Each of these teams will have team members (Employees) and a Project Manager. This data will be used for "My Group" concept : It would be used for managing information of a group that the party is member of.
